item.title: DOUBLES SQUASH, IS THAT EVEN POSSIBLE!?
item.author: Hui-Ling Wong,David Newman,Patrick Brandl,
item.description: Yes, and it’s safe too! IC squash hosted our Inaugural Doubles Open at Ethos, with teams hailing from our own club, Imperial alumni, students from all the various London universities, and doubles enthusiasts enticed via social media.
